      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you my absolute pride and joy! This beauty is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been garage-kept and babied since day one, so you won't find a single scratch or dent anywhere. I\u2019m really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it! Come by and take a look, I promise you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
