    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional A80 chassis featuring the iconic 2JZ-GTE twin-scroll sequential turbocharged inline-six. This specimen maintains its factory-spec V160 Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring authentic power delivery and longitudinal stability. The engine bay is concours-level, with all vacuum lines, heat shields, and VIN tags intact. Suspension remains the original double-wishbone configuration, offering precise kinematics without the fatigue typical of high-mileage units. Every component, from the magnesium valve covers to the four-piston front calipers, reflects a rigorous maintenance schedule. This is a collector-grade example with zero modifications, presenting a rare opportunity for the JDM purist.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
