    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been maintained to the highest possible standards. The exterior is finished in a flawless coat with a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. It has been kept in a climate-controlled garage and recently treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating for lasting protection. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with absolutely no bolster wear or creasing, and the factory floor mats have been protected by weather-proof liners since day one. Every technological feature, from the advanced driver-assistance systems to the premium infotainment suite, functions with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is peerless. It comes with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full fluid exchange and a comprehensive multi-point inspection that returned a perfect bill of health. The tires are near-new with 90% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, immediate stopping power. For the buyer seeking a turn-key, collector-grade experience without the showroom price tag, this vehicle stands alone.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
